{"tid":211640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎放低一個人生中既過客","createTime":"2017-04-21T18:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T03:59:52.000Z","uid":81812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9c2489e8d6486e292fa812eea3f965fff9662e","tid":211640,"uid":81812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:33:35.000Z","msg":"我先,前幾年我讀書果時識左一個師姐<br />\n一開始佢先開始同我傾計<br />\n其實真係傾左好心事又傾得好開心好似做左閨密咁<br />\n唔知點解又會鍾意左佢<br />\n結果佢畢業果時同左佢表白,但係佢話唔鍾意細過佢既男仔<br />\n自此就冇再傾過計<br />\n而家就算有時係街見到,都只會尷尬咁微笑下<br />\n然後如跌落地下既玻璃咁各散東西<br />\nsor for 1999"},{"pid":"33a50249e609493175e01e67aee568d7e070edba","tid":211640,"uid":81812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:35:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b21a10adfcf67e132fc09f0b29b17bbfd5eb7a0a","tid":211640,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:39:21.000Z","msg":"本身best fd但佢有男朋友就無再搵我了 好似比人利用咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來無左個best fd同失戀嘅感覺係咁接近"},{"pid":"73463f7ee834de139ab4319077f2096dbc7ed01a","tid":211640,"uid":100822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"小學校長，嗰陣家境唔好，幫咗好多。但好耐冇聯絡，最近先知去咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a0691ac401bae1f645622586a1ca052a05c54a","tid":211640,"uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:44:28.000Z","msg":"前度<br />\n<br />\n教我學識點樣去愛"},{"pid":"c7d0c44d2ed3d16b8ac104507f259e5e590dcb89","tid":211640,"uid":81812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學校長，嗰陣家境唔好，幫咗好多。但好耐冇聯絡，最近先知去咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><